Ms. H. Thi Hoa, born in 1963 (Ms 10030019 ), loan amount requesting 240 USD to raise chickens, ducks and buy produce. Her husband works as hired help to supplement their income. Her family's main business is agriculture and raising livestock. Her family's average income is 180 USD per month. She is also active in the community; she is always enthusiastic and happy so everyone loves her and thus she is the leader of her group of loan members. The other members are:

Ms. T. Thi Ly, born in 1965 (Ms 10030017 ), loan amount requesting 240 USD to purchase merchandise;
Ms. D. Thi Khanh, born in 1973 (Ms 10030021), loan amount requesting 240 USD to raise pigs;
Ms. N. Thi Oanh, unknown year of birth, (Ms 10030022), loan amount requesting 240 USD to invest in her barber shop;
Ms. H. Thi Hai, born in 1969 (Ms 10030025 ), loan amount requesting 135 USD to raise pigs and buy produce;
Ms. T. Thi Chin, born in 1976 (Ms 10030018 ), loan amount requesting 240 USD to invest in her refreshment shop;
Ms. H. Thi Chuyen, born in 1964 (Ms 10030020), loan amount requesting 240 USD to raise pigs and buy produce 




